Text: Feel free to ask any questions you may have. I couldn't get the game to work with the 1.4 patch, but 1.497 seemed to work great once I disabled landscape bump-mapping.

Hey all, feedback is encouraged . . . I'd like to know if everything worked out. I've noticed a few have downloaded, it, and we even have some seeders other than my self, but I would like to know if the ISO's both worked properly, and if anyone actually did find a later version of Gamespy Arcade.
